   What is a good name for the variable x, found in the code block below?

   .. code-block:: cpp

    #include <iostream>
    using namespace std;

    int main() {
      int x = 1;
      while (x <= 6) {
        cout << 2*x << "   ";
        x = x + 1;
      }
      cout << endl;
      return 0;
    }